text:
@faz3 ‘tis wonderful oh thy presence;
my dearest Prince of serenity;
 truly a godsend to this 💜 of mine; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 how kind be the clouds for their kindness;
the day be fine be so uplifting;
thou art in my mind and especially in one’s 💜;
day by day this devotion be only stronger; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 this be my happy place;
thou art my tranquility;
time be the currency of life;
with my dearest Prince;
it’d be my precious;
one holds in one’s 💜; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@fazzamohamed0175 أتابعك من يوم قلبي عرفك،
ومن يوم شفتك صار يومي عيد…
وأنت أكيد تعرف🤍♥️ من جد مسائي الحمداني👏🌹

@fazzamohamed0175 فيه سعيد وفيه عيد،
واللي يبقى أكيد… هو المحبة والوديد.
حتى إنستغرام يقول: لالا كثير! 😄 من جد بتتكلم👏👏👏 خليني اقوم  نفسي وظبط نفسي عشان ما تشوف شوش لا تتكلم جد و الله

@faz3 the wish of this 💜;
is lovingly kept;
the passing of time
but still one’s here;
despite the silence;
and us being apart;
oh this forlorn love;
is aching for thee;
my dearest Prince; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🕊️🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 in times of longing;
this 💜 sighs if only my dearest Prince be here;
and the longing be
each time I look upon thy face;
and that voice of thine;
makes one reach out (to thee) much, much more; 🚴🐎🐪🦒🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 thinking of thee on this quiet afternoon;
feeling the tranquility with thy presence;
contemplating this existence with its limited quality;
but with quality nonetheless; 💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🐠🐥🌳☕️📷💙

@faz3 ☕️ love to my dearest Prince;
on this day under the sun;
thy presence is truly a godsend;
thank heavens for thy strength and awesomeness; 💜🚴🐎🐪🦒🐠🐥🌳📷💙
